OL,3,CNHS 'overwhelmed' and 'close to
OL,4,Ccollapse' during pandemic, Covid
OL,5,Cinquiry finds
OL,7,FWords by Producer Eva Carroll
OL,9,FThe UK's healthcare system "came close
OL,10,Fto collapse" and "coped, but only
OL,11,Fjust", the chair of the UK Covid-19
OL,12,FInquiry said.
OL,14,FThe inquiry found that the UK entered
OL,15,Fthe pandemic ill-prepared, with its
OL,16,Foverstretched healthcare systems in a
OL,17,Fprecarious state and recognises that
OL,18,Fit was "unsurprising that the impact
OL,19,Fof the pandemic was devastating".
OL,26,@qD@\OUrD@LO]rD@ROUsD@EO]zD@HOU{D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773964972
OL,3,CNHS 'overwhelmed' and 'close to
OL,4,Ccollapse' during pandemic, Covid
OL,5,Cinquiry finds
OL,7,FDespite the best efforts of healthcare
OL,8,Fworkers, many Covid patients did not
OL,9,Freceive the care they would otherwise
OL,10,Freceive and non Covid patients had
OL,11,Ftheir diagnoses and treatment delayed.
OL,13,FChair of the Inquiry, Baroness Heather
OL,14,FHallet, concluded: "The healthcare
OL,15,Fsystems came close to collapse.
OL,16,FHealthcare workers carried the burden
OL,17,Fof caring for the sick in
OL,18,Funprecedented numbers
OL,26,@vD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
