CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773964972
OL,3,CNHS 'overwhelmed' and 'close to
OL,4,Ccollapse' during pandemic, Covid
OL,5,Cinquiry finds
OL,7,F"It came at a huge cost to them, their
OL,8,Ffamilies, their patients and the loved
OL,9,Fones of patients. Collapse was only
OL,10,Fnarrowly avoided thanks to the
OL,11,Fextraordinary efforts of all those
OL,12,Fworking in healthcare across the UK."
OL,14,FMore than 300 written statements and
OL,15,F300,000 pages of evidence were
OL,16,Freceived.
OL,18,FOver the ten week hearing in the
OL,19,Fautumn of 2024, 93 witnesses gave
OL,20,Fevidence.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
