OL,3,CNHS 'overwhelmed' and 'close to
OL,4,Ccollapse' during pandemic, Covid
OL,5,Cinquiry finds
OL,7,FThe inquiry identified that
OL,8,Fpoliticians, including the then Health
OL,9,FSecretary Matt Hancock, were reluctant
OL,10,Fto accept that healthcare systems were
OL,11,F"overwhelmed", as they chose this to
OL,12,Fmean total collapse.
OL,14,FLady Hallet suggested this was a
OL,15,Fquestion of "semantics", and that
OL,16,Fhealthcare systems were placed under
OL,17,Fintolerable strain regardless of the
OL,18,Fwords used to describe it by ministers.
OL,26,@wD@MOUwD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
