OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773964972
OL,3,CNHS 'overwhelmed' and 'close to
OL,4,Ccollapse' during pandemic, Covid
OL,5,Cinquiry finds
OL,7,FAccording to the inquiry, supplies of
OL,8,Fadequate PPE were limited, causing
OL,9,Fhealthcare workers to sometimes work
OL,10,Fin unsuitable PPE and put themselves
OL,11,Fand their families at risk to care for
OL,12,Fpatients.
OL,14,FHealthcare workers put their lives at
OL,15,Frisk and the pandemic had a
OL,16,Fsignificant and long-lasting impact on
OL,17,Ftheir mental health and wellbeing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
