CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773964972
OL,3,CNHS 'overwhelmed' and 'close to
OL,4,Ccollapse' during pandemic, Covid
OL,5,Cinquiry finds
OL,7,FProfessor Kevin Fong, a frontline NHS
OL,8,Fworker, told ITV News that he spoke to
OL,9,Fa member of NHS staff who described
OL,10,Fthe situation "like a terrorist attack
OL,11,Fevery day" because of the "urgent
OL,12,Fsurge" of patients - some of whom were
OL,13,Fthe "sickest" they had ever seen.
OL,15,FThis meant that lower levels of care
OL,16,Fwere provided to patients, and
OL,17,Fpatients did not always receive the
OL,18,Fcare they needed, despite the efforts
OL,19,Fof healthcare workers.
OL,26,@rD@OOUsD@JO]sD@[OUtD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
