OL,3,CNHS 'overwhelmed' and 'close to
OL,4,Ccollapse' during pandemic, Covid
OL,5,Cinquiry finds
OL,7,FThe inquiry concluded that visiting
OL,8,Frestrictions put in place meant that
OL,9,Fmany patients died without the comfort
OL,10,Fof being surrounded by their loved
OL,11,Fones.
OL,13,FIn addition, vulnerable patients, such
OL,14,Fas those with dementia, a learning
OL,15,Fdisability, and women accessing
OL,16,Fmaternity services, were left without
OL,17,Fvital support.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
