OL,3,CNHS 'overwhelmed' and 'close to
OL,4,Ccollapse' during pandemic, Covid
OL,5,Cinquiry finds
OL,7,FCatherine Todd, part of Northern
OL,8,FIreland Covid-19 Bereaved Families for
OL,9,FJustice, told the inquiry about the
OL,10,Fdeath of her newborn son, Ziggy, in
OL,11,Fthe pandemic.
OL,13,F"It was beyond distressing that we
OL,14,Fwere required to wear PPE to visit
OL,15,FZiggy, and to have photos with him
OL,16,Ftaken while we were wearing PPE, I do
OL,17,Fnot understand the reasoning behind
OL,18,Fthis.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773964972
OL,3,CNHS 'overwhelmed' and 'close to
OL,4,Ccollapse' during pandemic, Covid
OL,5,Cinquiry finds
OL,7,F"This has obviously had a very lasting
OL,8,Fimpact, and we are reminded of this
OL,9,Fevery time we look at any photos with
OL,10,Fhim."
OL,12,FThe inquiry made ten recommendations
OL,13,Fand suggested that they are all
OL,14,Fnecessary to prevent healthcare
OL,15,Fsystems from being overwhelmed in the
OL,16,Fnext pandemic.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@EO]
