OL,3,CNHS 'overwhelmed' and 'close to
OL,4,Ccollapse' during pandemic, Covid
OL,5,Cinquiry finds
OL,7,FAmong the recommendations are an
OL,8,Fincreased capacity in urgent and
OL,9,Femergency care, increased support for
OL,10,Fhealthcare workers, and improved data
OL,11,Fcollection to help identify high-risk
OL,12,Fgroups.
OL,14,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
