OL,3,CNHS 'overwhelmed' and 'close to
OL,4,Ccollapse' during pandemic, Covid
OL,5,Cinquiry finds
OL,7,FResponding to Thursday's publication,
OL,8,Fthe Covid-19 Bereaved Families group
OL,9,Furged the government to act on these,
OL,10,Fsaying "this report must not be left
OL,11,Fto gather dust".
OL,13,FIn a statement, they wrote: "It
OL,14,Fshouldn't take the deaths of our loved
OL,15,Fones or the tragic death of young
OL,16,Fpeople at university to put public
OL,17,Fhealth back on the political agenda.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
