OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1773964972
OL,3,CNHS 'overwhelmed' and 'close to
OL,4,Ccollapse' during pandemic, Covid
OL,5,Cinquiry finds
OL,7,F"The meningitis outbreak underlines
OL,8,Fwhy restoring resilience and capacity
OL,9,Fto our health system should be a
OL,10,Fmatter of priority for those in power.
OL,12,F"That's why what happens now is so
OL,13,Fimportant."
OL,15,FThe UK Covid-19 Inquiry's next report
OL,16,Fwill focus on the implementation of
OL,17,Fthe vaccine rollout, which will be
OL,18,Fpublished next month, with a further
OL,19,Ffour reports to follow.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
